Package: nof1power
Title: Power Analysis and Simulation for N-of-1 Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: Power analysis and simulation tools for N-of-1 clinical trial designs.
    Provides functions for sample size calculation, power estimation, and
    Monte Carlo simulation of N-of-1 crossover trials. Built as a reproducible
    research compendium using the zzcollab framework.
